'''Nano missiles''',<ref name="SF">[[Star Wars: Starfighter (video game)|''Star Wars: Starfighter'']]</ref> also known as '''nano-missles''',<ref name="TCSWE">{{CSWECite|II|359|nano-missile}}</ref> were small projectile weapons, which were nearly indistinguishable from blaster bolts. Coupled with tracking technology,<ref name="SF" /> such as an [[ion encumbrance system]],<ref name="TCSWE" /> they were able to home in on enemy craft.<ref name="SF" /> They were utilized by several types of [[Starfighter/Legends|starfighter]] used by the [[Galactic Republic/Legends|Republic]].<ref name="TCSWE" />

[[Vana Sage]]'s ''[[Guardian Mantis]]'' was equipped with nano missiles, which were coupled with a shield disabling tracker for maximum effect.<ref name="SF" />

